			<td align="left" valign="top"><p>Dear Sir or Madam</p>

			
<p>The Challenge is the largest provider of NCS, an intense youth and community programme. We recruit seasonal staff to work on the NCS programme in various roles working with 15-17 year olds both residentially and non-residentially. For this reason we ask all potential staff to provide contact details for referees who can indicate their suitability to work on the programme.</p>

<p><strong>One of our candidates, [contact name], has named you as one of their referees.</strong></p>

<p>Please reply to this email, giving a character reference for the candidate and indicating their suitability to work with young people. Please consider the following in your response:</p>

<p><strong>A -</strong> Would this candidate provide a strong role model?</p>

<p><strong>B -</strong> Is the candidate organised and enthusiastic?</p>

<p><strong>C -</strong> Is the candidate energetic and positive?</p>

<p><strong>D -</strong> Would you be happy with this person to work with young people?</p>

<p>If you have any questions in regard to this reference request, please contact staffing.support@the-challenge.org.</p>

<p>Thank you for your time and co-operation!</p>

<p>Best wishes,</p>

<p>The Challenge</p>

<p>Email reference: CR 7.2.1</p>
